      <h2>Contact DK App Tools</h2>
      <p>For support, send an email with the app name, device details, and a short description of what happened.</p>
      <a class="support-email-link" href="mailto:dkapps.support@proton.me">Email support</a>
      <a class="support-email-address" href="mailto:dkapps.support@proton.me">dkapps.support@proton.me</a>
    </div>
    <div class="support-investigate">
      <h2>What helps us investigate</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>App name</li>
        <li>Device model and Android version</li>
        <li>What action you tried</li>
        <li>Any message shown by the app</li>
        <li>Whether the issue happens every time</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Screenshots can help, but avoid showing private files, passwords, access codes, recovery information, or sensitive personal data.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

