  <section class="compact-panel support-section support-boundary-panel">
    <div class="support-section-head">
      <h2>Support and privacy boundaries</h2>
      <p>DK App Tools can help with app behavior, troubleshooting, product questions, and privacy questions. Support can only review the information you choose to provide. Some app data may remain only on your device, depending on the product.</p>
